ADDITIONAL NOTICE — PSX market data

This software fetches publicly accessible data from the Pakistan Stock
Exchange Data Portal (dps.psx.com.pk). PSX market data is licensed for
personal and non-commercial use only. Operators of this software are
responsible for their own use of that data. Do not redistribute or resell
PSX market data without a license from PSX
(marketdatarequest@psx.com.pk).

The MIT license above applies to the source code in this repository, not to
any data scraped at runtime.
